      "special_instructions": "CRITICAL: The goal is not just listing rhetorical features but understanding the strategic whole. How do all the pieces work together? What's the overall persuasive strategy? What drama is really being staged? Burke says all rhetoric is about identification - who is being recruited into what 'we'?"
